## ⚠️ Common Issues

### 1. No QR appears

* Check UART wiring
* Ensure common GND
* Verify baud rate = 115200

### 2. Garbage serial output

* Noise or wrong wiring
* Loose connections

### 3. ESP32-CAM resets

* Power issue → use stable 5V supply

